This demo performed using azure virtual machine

1.Spin up Azure virtual machine
	- inbound ports HTTP, HTTPS, SSH
	- if required add RDP 

2. login via ssh 

3. sudo apache2 service install

sudo su

sudo apt update
sudo apt install apache2 -y

4.enable service while login

sudo systemctl enable apache2

5.reboot the machine

Additional cmds: - 
check status of service
sudo systemctl status apache2

manullay start and stop as service
sudo systemctl start apache2
sudo systemctl stop apache2
